beer.beer_description: Long Reef Pale draws its inspiration from the Australian Surf culture and our local Long Reef beach. A massive pacific hop burst, with hops exclusively added late in the boil in a unprecedented mix of true Pacific hop fragrance and flavour. Combining the likes of Summer and Galaxy hops, this beer delivers a great new Pale Ale experience that is delivers at every sip.
